	<pb facs="liv_000085_0001" n="0001"/><!-- Change and repeat as necessary. Always indent <pb>, as here. -->
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><add place="marginleft" hand="#U" rend="blue diagonal">836</add><!-- Inside white sticker --> <space extent="2" unit="words"/><settlement type="village">Ukhonongo</settlement> <date when="1873-10">October 1873</date><!-- Text goes here --></p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p>Sir</p>
<lb/><p><space extent="1" unit="words"/>We have <choice><sic>heared</sic><corr>heard</corr></choice> in the month
<lb/>of <date when="1873-08">August</date> that you have started from
<lb/><geogName type="island">Zanzibar</geogName> for <settlement type="town"><choice><sic>Unnyenyembe</sic><corr>Unyanyembe</corr></choice></settlement>, and again
<lb/>and again<!-- Not sure if this repetition is a mistake or choice, so leaving as is. AW --> lately we have <choice><sic>heared</sic><corr>heard</corr></choice> <choice><sic>your</sic><corr>you</corr></choice>
<lb/><choice><sic>arrivd</sic><corr>arrived</corr></choice> - your father<!-- David Livingstone --> died by <term type="ailment">disease</term>
<lb/>beyond the <region>country of <term type="ethnic-group">Bisa</term></region>, but we have
<lb/>carried the corpse with us, 10 of our <term type="occupation">soldiers</term>
<lb/>are lost and some have died. Our <w>h<subst><del>a</del><add place="over-text">u</add></subst>n<add place="above">ger</add></w>
<lb/>presses us to aks you for some clothes
<lb/>to buy provision for our <term type="occupation">soldiers</term>
<lb/>and we should have an answer that
<lb/>when we shall enter there shall be firing
<lb/>guns or not, and if you permit us
<lb/>to fire guns, then send some powder
<lb/>We have <choice><sic>wrote</sic><corr>written</corr></choice> these few words in the place 
<lb/>of <persName><roleName>Sultan</roleName> or <roleName>king</roleName> Mbowra</persName></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="5" unit="words"/>The <persName><roleName>writer</roleName> Jacob Wainwright</persName></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="6" unit="words"/><hi rend="double-underline"><orgName><persName><roleName>D<hi rend="sup dotted-underline">r</hi></roleName> Livingstone</persName> <choice><abbr>Exped</abbr><expan>Expedition</expan></choice></orgName></hi></p>


